      <title>亿万富翁 Tykac 拒绝 ESG 推动，在全球范围内押注肮脏煤炭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/billionaire-tykac-bucks-esg-push-with-global-bet-on-dirty-coal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当大多数投资者放弃煤炭时，捷克亿万富翁帕维尔·蒂卡茨 (Pavel Tykac) 却加倍投资这种污染严重的燃料——只不过不是在自己的祖国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/billionaire-tykac-bucks-esg-push-with-global-bet-on-dirty-coal</guid>
